Optics Simulator
================

This is an optical process simulator, capable of simulating the movement of light through various media.
It should be capable of replicating optical phenomena on all scales, including phenomena such as diffraction.

Installing
==========

This library uses cmake.
You may need to make adjustments on a non-Posix system to build.
To build and install use:

mkdir build && cd build
cmake ..
make
sudo make install

Dependancies
============

If you build with -DGRAPHICS=1, which provides a graphical interface to the software, you will need:
-OpenGL
-GLFW

